<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Maiden" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Maiden,</orth> 1) virgin: <cit><quote>then are you no m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 88</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.175" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 175</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.4.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 4, 75</bibl>. Oftenest adjectively: <cit><quote>the m. burning of his cheeks,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 50" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 50</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. worlds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 408" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 408</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>bud,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 408" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 408</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. son 16.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 16, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.66.6" default="NO" valid="yes">66, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.154.4" default="NO" valid="yes">154, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.4.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 4, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.109" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 109</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.166" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.166" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 166</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.351" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 351</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.351" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 351</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.164" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 164</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.285" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 285</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.2.57" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 2, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.253" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 253</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.253" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 253</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.253" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 253</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.47" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.52" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.169" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.5.41" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.232" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 232</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.86" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 86</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.256" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 256</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 5.1.243" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 1, 243</bibl>. <cit><quote>a m. and an innocent hand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.252" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 252</bibl></cit> (not yet stained with blood). <cit><quote>thy m. sword,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.134" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 134</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. youth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.7.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 7, 38</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) girl: <cit><quote>--s' eyes stuck over all his face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lc 81" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 81</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.4.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 4, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.916" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 916</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 35</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.74" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 74</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 3, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.5.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Sh